This will insert 3 sample records with:
- Different IDs (MD001, MD002, MD003)
- Different publication and contact IDs
- Mix of PENDING and SENT statuses 
- Staggered send_after times (1, 2, and 3 hours from now)
- Created by SYSTEM
- Current timestamp for created_date
- NULL values for modification fields

You can verify the data with:
```sql
SELECT * FROM mobile_distribution ORDER BY send_after;
